    "The resulting test set contained 105 positive notes (prevalence=0.18).In addition to the test set, we prepared a development set of 600 notes that was used to aid the development of the labeler model.",
    "This set was manually labeled by a single data scientist, using a labeling guideline (Multimedia Appendix 1) that was developed as part of the test set generation.",
    "The development set contained 100 positive notes (preva-lence=0.17).",
    "Labeler Model DerivationWe then derived a labeler model that used weak supervision to probabilistically assign labels for the training set.",
